Package: srm
Type: Package
Title: Methods for Calculating Image Surface Roughness Metrics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Annie C. Smith
Maintainer: Annie C. Smith <coope378@msu.edu>
Description: Methods for calculating image roughness parameters
    as found in McGarigal et al. (2009), Kedron et al. (2018),
    and Dahlin et al. (in prep). Options for plotting are included.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
Imports: 
    dplyr (>= 0.7.8),
    gstat (>= 1.1-6),
    MASS (>= 7.3-51.1),
    phonTools (>= 0.2-2.1),
    plotly (>= 4.8.0),
    plotrix (>= 3.7-4),
    pracma (>= 2.2.2),
    raster (>= 2.8-4),
    signal (>= 0.7-6),
    spatial (>= 7.3-11),
    spatstat (>= 1.57-1),
    tibble (>= 1.4.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
